headline: International Paper Chairman and CEO to Speak at the Citi 2024 Basic Materials Conference
summary: International Paper Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Andy Silvernail will speak at the Citi 2024 Basic Materials Conference on December 4, 2024. The presentation is scheduled to begin at 8 a.m. Eastern time and will be followed by a question-and-answer session.
